Output .github/demo.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 800
Set Height 500
Set Padding 20
Set Theme "Catppuccin Macchiato"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

Type "gh auth status"
Enter
Sleep 4s

Ctrl+L
Sleep 500ms

Type "cd ~/personal-repo"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "ghx version"
Enter
Sleep 4s

Ctrl+L
Sleep 500ms

Type "cd ~/work-repo"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "ghx version"
Enter
Sleep 4s

Sleep 2s
